{"tid":1997520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐疫情大掙1000萬","createTime":"2020-05-01T17:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T17:15:54.000Z","uid":212449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a891ebbf95aa5a9148ca62f5267bbd96c6e37f7","tid":1997520,"uid":212449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續緩和，二手樓市明顯升溫，近日市場錄得多宗業主反價賣樓個案。市場消息透露，九龍站君臨天下2座低層D室，實用面積794平方呎，屬於2房連士多房間隔，業主原本叫價2280萬放盤，剛反價20萬以2300萬元易手，呎價28967元，屬於市價水平。<br />\n<br />\n有指單位原業主為前港姐冠軍曹敏莉的丈夫，早於2009年以1562萬元購入，持貨11年帳面獲利738萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2632563?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2632563%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw16CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=ed424db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2632563?r=cpstni</a>"},{"pid":"97915de207058120ea6ddb53446158fb79ef0fcd","tid":1997520,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"(2300/1562)^(1/11) = 1.03580256563<br />\n其實係賺咗住/租金<br />\n個資產本身冇乜得賺"}]}